$. In some cases we find large\noscillations (\"wiggles\") in the self-force shortly after periastron passage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 17:14:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2017 02:04:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-03"}
