 the mantle. In this regime, we\nobserve for the first time that plumes arise from a thick boundary with\ncellular structure and develop into sheet-plumes. We use experimental data to\nquantify these morphological changes and mixing dynamics of the plumes at\ndifferent regimes of U. We also compare our observations on plume spacing with\nvarious models reported in the literature by varying the viscosity ratio and\nthe buoyancy flux.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 19:03:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-01"}
