mic simulations (EAGLE, Illustris). The obscuration\nfrom ray-traced galaxy gas can agree with observations, but is highly sensitive\nto the chosen feedback assumptions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 20:00:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-11"}
