 In\nparticular the reader will notice the relevance of this result for the\ndevelopment of a theory of 2-topoi.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 23:43:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Jan 2017 22:36:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 18 May 2018 22:27:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-22"}
