obtain a near optimal solution. Finally, numerical results show that the\nproposed solutions achieve better performance than existing solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 29 Oct 2016 15:27:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 15 Jul 2017 00:47:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-18"}
